New Tricks
Mon 28 Jul, 9:00 pm - 10:00 pm 60mins

Loyalties and Royalties 

Gerry Standing meets his heroes, 70s rock band Bad Faith, when the team reinvestigate the death of lead guitarist Andy Fletcher. It is more than 30 years since the group&#039;s success and subsequent split following Fletcher&#039;s death, and the ageing rockers don&#039;t quite live up to the legends Gerry remembers. Determined to prevent UCOS disbanding, Brian finally tracks down Jack and tries to persuade him to return. Some strong language. [AD,S]
